Steps in launching a new website

launch instance
update packages
install lamp stack
configure mariadb
install wordpress
upload divi theme
customize theme
provision and asssociate elastic ip addr
set domain name to point to EIP address
setup ssl/tls

setup email address(es)
- if wordpress, connect forms to mail (smtp) service

If wordpress - 
    fix mixed content issue (plugin, manual replace)
    hide header (divi)
    set static homepage

